{
  "video_id": "LcNvkhS4UYg",
  "title": "3 kinds of bias that shape your worldview | J. Marshall Shepherd",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12952.0,
      "end_time": 14714.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a meteorologist by degree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14738.0,
      "end_time": 17881.0,
      "text": "I have a bachelor&#39;s, master&#39;s and PhD in physical meteorology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17905.0,
      "end_time": 20410.0,
      "text": "so I&#39;m a meteorologist, card carrying."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20444.0,
      "end_time": 25143.0,
      "text": "And so with that comes four questions, always."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25167.0,
      "end_time": 27723.0,
      "text": "This is one prediction I will always get right."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27747.0,
      "end_time": 29603.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29627.0,
      "end_time": 31674.0,
      "text": "And those questions are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31699.0,
      "end_time": 34183.0,
      "text": "\"Marshall, what channel are you on?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34207.0,
      "end_time": 36240.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36480.0,
      "end_time": 38889.0,
      "text": "\"Dr. Shepherd, what&#39;s the weather going to be tomorrow?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38913.0,
      "end_time": 39913.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39937.0,
      "end_time": 41524.0,
      "text": "And oh, I love this one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41548.0,
      "end_time": 44993.0,
      "text": "\"My daughter is getting married next September, it&#39;s an outdoor wedding."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45170.0,
      "end_time": 46227.0,
      "text": "Is it going to rain?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46251.0,
      "end_time": 47632.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47657.0,
      "end_time": 50562.0,
      "text": "Not kidding, I get those, and I don&#39;t know the answer to that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50586.0,
      "end_time": 52186.0,
      "text": "the science isn&#39;t there."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53185.0,
      "end_time": 56880.0,
      "text": "But the one I get a lot these days is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56112.0,
      "end_time": 60964.0,
      "text": "\"Dr. Shepherd, do you believe in climate change?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61331.0,
      "end_time": 64370.0,
      "text": "\"Do you believe in global warming?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64807.0,
      "end_time": 68506.0,
      "text": "Now, I have to gather myself every time I get that question."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68530.0,
      "end_time": 70292.0,
      "text": "Because it&#39;s an ill-posed question --"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 70316.0,
      "end_time": 72316.0,
      "text": "science isn&#39;t a belief system."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72911.0,
      "end_time": 76177.0,
      "text": "My son, he&#39;s 10 -- he believes in the tooth fairy."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76998.0,
      "end_time": 80387.0,
      "text": "And he needs to get over that, because I&#39;m losing dollars, fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80411.0,
      "end_time": 82728.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82752.0,
      "end_time": 84577.0,
      "text": "But he believes in the tooth fairy."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84601.0,
      "end_time": 86572.0,
      "text": "But consider this."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87361.0,
      "end_time": 89909.0,
      "text": "Bank of America building, there, in Atlanta."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89933.0,
      "end_time": 92488.0,
      "text": "You never hear anyone say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92512.0,
      "end_time": 95910.0,
      "text": "\"Do you believe, if you go to the top of that building"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95115.0,
      "end_time": 97369.0,
      "text": "and throw a ball off, it&#39;s going to fall?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 97807.0,
      "end_time": 101141.0,
      "text": "You never hear that, because gravity is a thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102427.0,
      "end_time": 104712.0,
      "text": "So why don&#39;t we hear the question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104736.0,
      "end_time": 106541.0,
      "text": "\"Do you believe in gravity?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 106565.0,
      "end_time": 108423.0,
      "text": "But of course, we hear the question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108447.0,
      "end_time": 110780.0,
      "text": "\"Do you believe in global warming?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 112161.0,
      "end_time": 114573.0,
      "text": "Well, consider these facts."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115799.0,
      "end_time": 118895.0,
      "text": "The American Association for the Advancement of Science, AAAS,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118919.0,
      "end_time": 121768.0,
      "text": "one of the leading organizations in science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121792.0,
      "end_time": 125712.0,
      "text": "queried scientists and the public on different science topics."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125736.0,
      "end_time": 126935.0,
      "text": "Here are some of them:"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126959.0,
      "end_time": 130886.0,
      "text": "genetically modified food, animal research, human evolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 131709.0,
      "end_time": 134209.0,
      "text": "And look at what the scientists say about those,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134233.0,
      "end_time": 136947.0,
      "text": "the people that actually study those topics, in red,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 136971.0,
      "end_time": 139598.0,
      "text": "versus the gray, what the public thinks."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 139622.0,
      "end_time": 141208.0,
      "text": "How did we get there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 141982.0,
      "end_time": 143474.0,
      "text": "How did we get there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144743.0,
      "end_time": 148644.0,
      "text": "That scientists and the public are so far apart on these science issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 151655.0,
      "text": "Well, I&#39;ll come a little bit closer to home for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 151680.0,
      "end_time": 152830.0,
      "text": "climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 153339.0,
      "end_time": 156231.0,
      "text": "Eighty-seven percent of scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 156255.0,
      "end_time": 160463.0,
      "text": "believe that humans are contributing to climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 161450.0,
      "end_time": 163716.0,
      "text": "But only 50 percent of the public?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 165323.0,
      "end_time": 166704.0,
      "text": "How did we get there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166728.0,
      "end_time": 168310.0,
      "text": "So it begs the question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168550.0,
      "end_time": 172792.0,
      "text": "what shapes perceptions about science?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 174655.0,
      "end_time": 176450.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an interesting question"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 176690.0,
      "end_time": 178647.0,
      "text": "and one that I&#39;ve been thinking about quite a bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 180434.0,
      "end_time": 185100.0,
      "text": "I think that one thing that shapes perceptions in the public, about science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 185124.0,
      "end_time": 187314.0,
      "text": "is belief systems and biases."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 188339.0,
      "end_time": 189775.0,
      "text": "Belief systems and biases."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 189799.0,
      "end_time": 191399.0,
      "text": "Go with me for a moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 192500.0,
      "end_time": 194458.0,
      "text": "Because I want to talk about three elements of that:"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 194482.0,
      "end_time": 198155.0,
      "text": "confirmation bias, Dunning-Kruger effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 198179.0,
      "end_time": 200440.0,
      "text": "and cognitive dissonance."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 200680.0,
      "end_time": 204910.0,
      "text": "Now, these sound like big, fancy, academic terms, and they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 204585.0,
      "end_time": 208212.0,
      "text": "But when I describe them, you&#39;re going to be like, \"Oh!"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 208236.0,
      "end_time": 211969.0,
      "text": "I recognize that; I even know somebody that does that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 213355.0,
      "end_time": 214934.0,
      "text": "Confirmation bias."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 220732.0,
      "text": "Finding evidence that supports what we already believe."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 220756.0,
      "end_time": 223680.0,
      "text": "Now, we&#39;re probably all a little bit guilty of that at times."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 225427.0,
      "end_time": 226965.0,
      "text": "Take a look at this."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 226990.0,
      "end_time": 228307.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m on Twitter."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 228331.0,
      "end_time": 230734.0,
      "text": "And often, when it snows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 230759.0,
      "end_time": 232648.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll get this tweet back to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 232672.0,
      "end_time": 235148.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 235172.0,
      "end_time": 238901.0,
      "text": "\"Hey, Dr. Shepherd, I have 20 inches of global warming in my yard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 238925.0,
      "end_time": 241909.0,
      "text": "what are you guys talking about, climate change?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 241933.0,
      "end_time": 243671.0,
      "text": "I get that tweet a lot, actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 244909.0,
      "end_time": 247846.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a cute tweet, it makes me chuckle as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 247870.0,
      "end_time": 251815.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s oh, so fundamentally scientifically flawed."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 252292.0,
      "end_time": 253850.0,
      "text": "Because it illustrates"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 253874.0,
      "end_time": 255894.0,
      "text": "that the person tweeting doesn&#39;t understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 255919.0,
      "end_time": 258210.0,
      "text": "the difference between weather and climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 259466.0,
      "end_time": 263140.0,
      "text": "I often say, weather is your mood"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 263380.0,
      "end_time": 265497.0,
      "text": "and climate is your personality."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 266981.0,
      "end_time": 268132.0,
      "text": "Think about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 268156.0,
      "end_time": 270600.0,
      "text": "Weather is your mood, climate is your personality."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 270624.0,
      "end_time": 274609.0,
      "text": "Your mood today doesn&#39;t necessarily tell me anything about your personality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 274633.0,
      "end_time": 277402.0,
      "text": "nor does a cold day tell me anything about climate change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 277427.0,
      "end_time": 279427.0,
      "text": "or a hot day, for that matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 281974.0,
      "end_time": 283123.0,
      "text": "Dunning-Kruger."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 283616.0,
      "end_time": 286671.0,
      "text": "Two scholars from Cornell came up with the Dunning-Kruger effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 286695.0,
      "end_time": 289750.0,
      "text": "If you go look up the peer-reviewed paper for this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 289100.0,
      "end_time": 291569.0,
      "text": "you will see all kinds of fancy terminology:"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 291593.0,
      "end_time": 295236.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s an illusory superiority complex, thinking we know things."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 298770.0,
      "text": "In other words, people think they know more than they do."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 299553.0,
      "end_time": 302486.0,
      "text": "Or they underestimate what they don&#39;t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 302847.0,
      "end_time": 305313.0,
      "text": "And then, there&#39;s cognitive dissonance."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 306831.0,
      "end_time": 309164.0,
      "text": "Cognitive dissonance is interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 309538.0,
      "end_time": 312188.0,
      "text": "We just recently had Groundhog Day, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 313132.0,
      "end_time": 315853.0,
      "text": "Now, there&#39;s no better definition of cognitive dissonance"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 315877.0,
      "end_time": 319395.0,
      "text": "than intelligent people asking me if a rodent&#39;s forecast is accurate."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 319419.0,
      "end_time": 322150.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 322174.0,
      "end_time": 324721.0,
      "text": "But I get that, all of the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 324745.0,
      "end_time": 325999.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 326230.0,
      "end_time": 329626.0,
      "text": "But I also hear about the Farmer&#39;s Almanac."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 329650.0,
      "end_time": 332846.0,
      "text": "We grew up on the Farmer&#39;s Almanac, people are familiar with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 334259.0,
      "end_time": 337671.0,
      "text": "The problem is, it&#39;s only about 37 percent accurate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 337695.0,
      "end_time": 340829.0,
      "text": "according to studies at Penn State University."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 343458.0,
      "end_time": 347290.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;re in an era of science"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 347530.0,
      "end_time": 349117.0,
      "text": "where we actually can forecast the weather."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 349141.0,
      "end_time": 352562.0,
      "text": "And believe it or not, and I know some of you are like, \"Yeah, right,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 352586.0,
      "end_time": 355609.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re about 90 percent accurate, or more, with weather forecast."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 355633.0,
      "end_time": 358257.0,
      "text": "You just tend to remember the occasional miss, you do."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 358281.0,
      "end_time": 359431.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 362263.0,
      "end_time": 365667.0,
      "text": "So confirmation bias, Dunning-Kruger and cognitive dissonance."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 365692.0,
      "end_time": 371104.0,
      "text": "I think those shape biases and perceptions that people have about science."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 371625.0,
      "end_time": 373774.0,
      "text": "But then, there&#39;s literacy and misinformation"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 373798.0,
      "end_time": 375865.0,
      "text": "that keep us boxed in, as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 377911.0,
      "end_time": 380395.0,
      "text": "During the hurricane season of 2017,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 380419.0,
      "end_time": 384632.0,
      "text": "media outlets had to actually assign reporters"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 384656.0,
      "end_time": 388813.0,
      "text": "to dismiss fake information about the weather forecast."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 390204.0,
      "end_time": 392138.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the era that we&#39;re in."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 392644.0,
      "end_time": 395810.0,
      "text": "I deal with this all the time in social media."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 395105.0,
      "end_time": 396692.0,
      "text": "Someone will tweet a forecast --"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 396716.0,
      "end_time": 399652.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s a forecast for Hurricane Irma, but here&#39;s the problem:"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 399676.0,
      "end_time": 401676.0,
      "text": "it didn&#39;t come from the Hurricane Center."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 402608.0,
      "end_time": 405395.0,
      "text": "But people were tweeting and sharing this; it went viral."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 405419.0,
      "end_time": 408284.0,
      "text": "It didn&#39;t come from the National Hurricane Center at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 410363.0,
      "end_time": 412847.0,
      "text": "So I spent 12 years of my career at NASA"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 412871.0,
      "end_time": 414902.0,
      "text": "before coming to the University of Georgia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 414927.0,
      "end_time": 417442.0,
      "text": "and I chair their Earth Science Advisory Committee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 417466.0,
      "end_time": 419283.0,
      "text": "I was just up there last week in DC."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 419307.0,
      "end_time": 421294.0,
      "text": "And I saw some really interesting things."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 421318.0,
      "end_time": 424556.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a NASA model and science data from satellite"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 424580.0,
      "end_time": 426863.0,
      "text": "showing the 2017 hurricane season."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 426887.0,
      "end_time": 428953.0,
      "text": "You see Hurricane Harvey there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 429649.0,
      "end_time": 432158.0,
      "text": "Look at all the dust coming off of Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 432617.0,
      "end_time": 437604.0,
      "text": "Look at the wildfires up in northwest US and in western Canada."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 437628.0,
      "end_time": 439428.0,
      "text": "There comes Hurricane Irma."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 440923.0,
      "end_time": 443660.0,
      "text": "This is fascinating to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 443688.0,
      "end_time": 445783.0,
      "text": "But admittedly, I&#39;m a weather geek."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 446982.0,
      "end_time": 450458.0,
      "text": "But more importantly, it illustrates that we have the technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 450482.0,
      "end_time": 453610.0,
      "text": "to not only observe the weather and climate system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 453850.0,
      "end_time": 454234.0,
      "text": "but predict it."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 454625.0,
      "end_time": 456387.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s scientific understanding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 456411.0,
      "end_time": 459498.0,
      "text": "so there&#39;s no need for some of those perceptions and biases"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 459522.0,
      "end_time": 461920.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;ve been talking about."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 461116.0,
      "end_time": 462315.0,
      "text": "We have knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 462339.0,
      "end_time": 463577.0,
      "text": "But think about this ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 463601.0,
      "end_time": 466783.0,
      "text": "This is Houston, Texas, after Hurricane Harvey."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 467736.0,
      "end_time": 470699.0,
      "text": "Now, I write a contribution for \"Forbes\" magazine periodically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 470733.0,
      "end_time": 475264.0,
      "text": "and I wrote an article a week before Hurricane Harvey made landfall, saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 475288.0,
      "end_time": 478130.0,
      "text": "\"There&#39;s probably going to be 40 to 50 inches of rainfall.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 478776.0,
      "end_time": 481260.0,
      "text": "I wrote that a week before it happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 481284.0,
      "end_time": 483409.0,
      "text": "But yet, when you talk to people in Houston,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 483434.0,
      "end_time": 486507.0,
      "text": "people are saying, \"We had no idea it was going to be this bad.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 487930.0,
      "end_time": 488268.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m just..."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 488292.0,
      "end_time": 489472.0,
      "text": "(Sigh)"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 489497.0,
      "end_time": 490633.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 490657.0,
      "end_time": 491830.0,
      "text": "A week before."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 491855.0,
      "end_time": 493450.0,
      "text": "But --"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 493690.0,
      "end_time": 495567.0,
      "text": "I know, it&#39;s amusing, but the reality is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 495591.0,
      "end_time": 501735.0,
      "text": "we all struggle with perceiving something outside of our experience level."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 501759.0,
      "end_time": 504290.0,
      "text": "People in Houston get rain all of the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 504530.0,
      "end_time": 505853.0,
      "text": "they flood all of the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 506513.0,
      "end_time": 508847.0,
      "text": "But they&#39;ve never experienced that."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 509561.0,
      "end_time": 513949.0,
      "text": "Houston gets about 34 inches of rainfall for the entire year."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 513974.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516529.00000000006,
      "text": "They got 50 inches in three days."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 517299.0,
      "end_time": 520390.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s an anomaly event, that&#39;s outside of the normal."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 522188.0,
      "end_time": 525290.0,
      "text": "So belief systems and biases, literacy and misinformation."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 525530.0,
      "end_time": 528936.0,
      "text": "How do we step out of the boxes that are cornering our perceptions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 530633.0,
      "end_time": 534366.0,
      "text": "Well we don&#39;t even have to go to Houston, we can come very close to home."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 534390.0,
      "end_time": 535571.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 535595.0,
      "end_time": 537508.0,
      "text": "Remember \"Snowpocalypse?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 537532.0,
      "end_time": 539333.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 539357.0,
      "end_time": 540857.0,
      "text": "Snowmageddon?"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 540881.0,
      "end_time": 542310.0,
      "text": "Snowzilla?"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 542560.0,
      "end_time": 544850.0,
      "text": "Whatever you want to call it."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 544109.0,
      "end_time": 546426.0,
      "text": "All two inches of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 546450.0,
      "end_time": 549530.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 549770.0,
      "end_time": 551942.0,
      "text": "Two inches of snow shut the city of Atlanta down."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 551966.0,
      "end_time": 553537.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 554982.0,
      "end_time": 559236.0,
      "text": "But the reality is, we were in a winter storm watch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 559260.0,
      "end_time": 561895.0,
      "text": "we went to a winter weather advisory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 561919.0,
      "end_time": 564569.0,
      "text": "and a lot of people perceived that as being a downgrade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 564593.0,
      "end_time": 566260.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, it&#39;s not going to be as bad.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 566284.0,
      "end_time": 569514.0,
      "text": "When in fact, the perception was that it was not going to be as bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 569538.0,
      "end_time": 571172.0,
      "text": "but it was actually an upgrade."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 571196.0,
      "end_time": 573783.0,
      "text": "Things were getting worse as the models were coming in."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 573807.0,
      "end_time": 577613.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s an example of how we get boxed in by our perceptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 578165.0,
      "end_time": 580141.0,
      "text": "So, the question becomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 580165.0,
      "end_time": 583656.0,
      "text": "how do we expand our radius?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 585823.0,
      "end_time": 587733.0,
      "text": "The area of a circle is \"pi r squared\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 587757.0,
      "end_time": 590000.0,
      "text": "We increase the radius, we increase the area."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 590240.0,
      "end_time": 594500.0,
      "text": "How do we expand our radius of understanding about science?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 594593.0,
      "end_time": 595992.0,
      "text": "Here are my thoughts."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 596720.0,
      "end_time": 599791.0,
      "text": "You take inventory of your own biases."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 599815.0,
      "end_time": 601831.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m challenging you all to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 601855.0,
      "end_time": 604879.0,
      "text": "Take an inventory of your own biases."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 604903.0,
      "end_time": 606188.0,
      "text": "Where do they come from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 606212.0,
      "end_time": 609586.0,
      "text": "Your upbringing, your political perspective, your faith --"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 609610.0,
      "end_time": 612290.0,
      "text": "what shapes your own biases?"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 613982.0,
      "end_time": 615419.0,
      "text": "Then, evaluate your sources --"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 615443.0,
      "end_time": 617894.0,
      "text": "where do you get your information on science?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 618553.0,
      "end_time": 620529.0,
      "text": "What do you read, what do you listen to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 620553.0,
      "end_time": 622553.0,
      "text": "to consume your information on science?"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 623220.0,
      "end_time": 625768.0,
      "text": "And then, it&#39;s important to speak out."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 625792.0,
      "end_time": 629910.0,
      "text": "Talk about how you evaluated your biases and evaluated your sources."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 629934.0,
      "end_time": 632704.0,
      "text": "I want you to listen to this little 40-second clip"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 632728.0,
      "end_time": 637506.0,
      "text": "from one of the top TV meteorologists in the US, Greg Fishel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 637530.0,
      "end_time": 639530.0,
      "text": "in the Raleigh, Durham area."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 639770.0,
      "end_time": 640752.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s revered in that region."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 640776.0,
      "end_time": 642180.0,
      "text": "But he was a climate skeptic."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 642205.0,
      "end_time": 644442.0,
      "text": "But listen to what he says about speaking out."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 644466.0,
      "end_time": 646202.0,
      "text": "Greg Fishel: The mistake I was making"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 646226.0,
      "end_time": 648180.0,
      "text": "and didn&#39;t realize until very recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 648204.0,
      "end_time": 650796.0,
      "text": "was that I was only looking for information"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 650821.0,
      "end_time": 653682.0,
      "text": "to support what I already thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 653706.0,
      "end_time": 657813.0,
      "text": "and was not interested in listening to anything contrary."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 658559.0,
      "end_time": 660630.0,
      "text": "And so I woke up one morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 660654.0,
      "end_time": 664352.0,
      "text": "and there was this question in my mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 664918.0,
      "end_time": 667522.0,
      "text": "\"Greg, are you engaging in confirmation bias?"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 667546.0,
      "end_time": 671471.0,
      "text": "Are you only looking for information to support what you already think?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 672690.0,
      "end_time": 674507.0,
      "text": "And if I was honest with myself, and I tried to be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 674522.0,
      "end_time": 676850.0,
      "text": "I admitted that was going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 677269.0,
      "end_time": 679783.0,
      "text": "And so the more I talked to scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 679807.0,
      "end_time": 681865.0,
      "text": "and read peer-reviewed literature"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 681889.0,
      "end_time": 686601.0,
      "text": "and tried to conduct myself the way I&#39;d been taught to conduct myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 686625.0,
      "end_time": 688958.0,
      "text": "at Penn State when I was a student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 689665.0,
      "end_time": 692357.0,
      "text": "it became very difficult for me to make the argument"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 692381.0,
      "end_time": 694440.0,
      "text": "that we weren&#39;t at least having some effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 694465.0,
      "end_time": 696901.0,
      "text": "Maybe there was still a doubt as to how much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 696925.0,
      "end_time": 701640.0,
      "text": "but to say \"nothing\" was not a responsible thing for me to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 701664.0,
      "end_time": 703464.0,
      "text": "as a scientist or a person."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 705387.0,
      "end_time": 709247.0,
      "text": "JMS: Greg Fishel just talked about expanding his radius"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 709272.0,
      "end_time": 710895.0,
      "text": "of understanding of science."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 710919.0,
      "end_time": 712973.0,
      "text": "And when we expand our radius,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 712998.0,
      "end_time": 716196.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not about making a better future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 716220.0,
      "end_time": 719287.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s about preserving life as we know it."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 720180.0,
      "end_time": 725133.0,
      "text": "So as we think about expanding our own radius in understanding science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 726292.0,
      "end_time": 729664.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s critical for Athens, Georgia, for Atlanta, Georgia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 729688.0,
      "end_time": 732545.0,
      "text": "for the state of Georgia, and for the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 732857.0,
      "end_time": 734928.0,
      "text": "So expand your radius."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 734952.0,
      "end_time": 736135.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 736159.0,
      "end_time": 740174.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}